  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK269">
<l>kūṟṟaṅ kutittaluṅ kaikūṭu nōṟṟali</l>
<l> ṉāṟṟa ṟalaippaṭṭa varkku.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have attained the power which religious discipline confers, will be able also to pass the limit of Yama, (the God of death).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
